title: Spiritual Solution For Every Problem (live) by Wayne W. Dyer
description: Spiritual Solution For Every Problem (live) by Wayne W. Dyer.  This is a live recording made before a live audience.  Unsure when and where it was recorded, but I believe it was around 2000.  The first six tracks are about 90 minutes long, each, so I split them into approximately 10 minute clips which is a lot friendlier if you have to stop in the middle of the clip.  Try fast forwarding 80 -85 minutes in your car and you&#039;ll see why i did that.  Enjoy, and please seed!!!
